Package com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.emx.processor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BulkAndForward
    A MessageSource that stores each incoming Message until no more messages arrive for an interval and then rapidly sends all of the stored messages in bulk.
    EMXDelimitedFileAdapter
    The EMXDelimitedFileAdapter is the visible facade of the EMXDelimitedFileSession class that deals with outgoing and incoming data files.
    EMXFileAdapter
    The EMXFileAdapter is the visible facade of some implementation of an EMXFileSession that deals with outgoing and incoming data files.
    EMXFileSession
    An instance of the EMXFileSession is created by an instance of an EMXFileAdapter and is linked to by all of the instances of EMXFileAdapter which serve the same party (typically two, one in the outgoing message processor chain and one in the incoming chain).
    EMXFileSession.Factory
    This class must be implemented by every concrete subclass of EMXFileSession.
    EMXMessageSigner
    The EMXMessageSigner is a MessageSource that signs all outgoing EMXMessages (except for messages that are being forwarded).
    EMXMessageUpCaster
    Note: This class need no longer be used.
    EMXMessageVerifier
    The EMXMessageVerifier is a MessageListener that can be configured to verify none, some or all incoming EMXMessages.
    MERRMessageUnwantedFieldStripper
    A Message Processor that strips unwanted fields from a provider- generated MERR message.
